{"tid":996512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到個伯伯之後有啲擔心自己之後老咗會變成咁","createTime":"2019-01-26T10:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T05:26:20.000Z","uid":214581,"like":62,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3b56169640f1284b2d093cb35f9aa7500ceec7a3","tid":996512,"uid":214581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"話說今日同朋友去深水埗行街<br />\n見肚餓就決定去食老M<br />\n上到去食緊嘢果陣係咁聞到陣臭味<br />\n望一望見到個伯伯坐咗喺度<br />\n個伯伯望落去似70鬆啲同埋好幾日冇食過嘢<br />\n因為見到佢係咁望住其他人食嘢<br />\n唔忍心見到佢挨餓就同我個朋友一齊夾錢買咗個餐俾佢食<br />\n買咗俾佢之後係咁多謝我<br />\n超驚自己老咗之後都係冇屋住、甚至連一餐飯都係問題"},{"pid":"86138620aa02df0f4841110cee52f4bc40550315","tid":996512,"uid":14606,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"以家香港真係生存都辛苦 見步行步啦"},{"pid":"d35d3a3caed09c8077cd1a9fd55e07bb5d152759","tid":996512,"uid":58054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"其實全部人都會變成咁<br />\n只係時間嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a15ad3bfe0f94d0947bde36a5f2517c741ef937","tid":996512,"uid":214581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d35d3a3caed09c8077cd1a9fd55e07bb5d152759","tid":996512,"uid":58054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"其實全部人都會變成咁<br />\n只係時間嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"唉 上到公屋已經算贏啦"},{"pid":"a3316c52a0c191bfa67d5029c43cf9af7488cc69","tid":996512,"uid":224452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:03:56.000Z","msg":"假若他日大家老癦相遇<br />\n吹吓水飲吓橙汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9967b6a8a2a512357bbf86cb72733f4b9b438d5c","tid":996512,"uid":214581,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a3316c52a0c191bfa67d5029c43cf9af7488cc69","tid":996512,"uid":224452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:03:56.000Z","msg":